        <p class="text-sm text-[#475569] leading-relaxed mb-3">All prices converted to USD at March 2026 exchange rates. Vendor markup estimates based on BuzzStream's methodology. Quality filtering follows BuzzStream's criteria: minimum 1,000 monthly organic traffic and minimum DR 40.</p>
